      "body" : "@davout:\r\nThe idea of having a wallet with 'only public keys', and thereby being able to monitor your balance while keeping your private keys secure, is a great idea :) but it is a /separate/ idea (and i think it deserves its own github issue).\r\n\r\nthe ability to import/export transactions would be useful independent of this 'public wallet' functionality. the 'public wallet' functionality would also be useful (but somewhat less so) without the tx import/export functionality.",
